  <Expressions>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="KeyStreaming">
      <expr><![CDATA[if (OneHasValue(ID_ISIN))
	return ID_ISIN;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_COMPANY))
	return ID_BB_COMPANY;
else if (OneHasValue(ISSUER_CMPID))
	return ISSUER_CMPID;
else if (OneHasValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE))
	return ID_BB_UNIQUE;
else
	return "";]]></expr>
    </Expression>
    <Expression enabled="true" ident="RecordIdentifier">
      <expr><![CDATA[if (Strcmp(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, "Equity"))
	if (AllHaveValue(TICKER, EQY_PRIM_EXCH_SHRT, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
		return Strcat(TICKER, Strcat(";", Strcat(EQY_PRIM_EXCH_SHRT,
				Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))))))));
	else if (AllHaveValue(SECURITIES, EQY_PRIM_EXCH_SHRT, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
		return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(EQY_PRIM_EXCH_SHRT,
				Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))))))));
	else
		return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))));
else if (AllHaveValue(ID_BB_UNIQUE, EXCH_CODE, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(ID_BB_UNIQUE, Strcat(";", Strcat(EXCH_CODE,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))))))));
else if (AllHaveValue(SECURITIES, EXCH_CODE, MARKET_SECTOR_DES))
	return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(EXCH_CODE,
			Strcat(";", Strcat(MARKET_SECTOR_DES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))))))));
else
	return Strcat(SECURITIES, Strcat(";", Strcat(ERRORCODE, Strcat(";", "PS"))));]]></expr>
    </Expression>
